author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Is TRON: Ares really that bad? Yes, actually. Is Witcher Season 4 already getting lambasted by fans? Yup. And does Predator Badlands look like a PG-13 joke? You bet. Join me, MauLer, Paul Chato, Little Platoon and Angry Badger for Open Bar 160. 

Subscribe to Paul: https://www.youtube.com/@CallMeChato
Subscribe to Platoon: https://www.youtube.com/@TheLittlePlatoon
Subscribe to Badger: https://www.youtube.com/@TheAngryBadger3
title: Open Bar #160 - TRON Ares Disaster, Witcher S4 Backlash, Predator Badlands
